deprecation.message: This package is Deprecated due to broken MessageBox and Growl. A new version with bug fixes will be released soon

description: Contains some simple and commonly used WPF controls based on HandyControl
releaseNotes:
Add Windows 11 SnapLayout
Add Windows 11 Mica Material (Can be used from Property in hc:Window or WindowHelper.EnableMicaEffect) 
Add Small Styles for controls (RepeatButton, ListBox, Treeview)
Add Support .Net6.0
Add TaskbarRebuildBehavior Class
Add ImageSelectedEvent for ImageSelector
Add Prev and Next Method for Coverflow
Add Boolean2VisibilityConverter
Add ShowMinButton/ShowMaxButton/ShowCloseButton Property for Window
Remove JumpTo method of ImageSelector
Public Some Theme.cs and ThemeResources.cs Methods
Public DpiHelper, IconHelper and ScreenHelper Classes
Upadte OSVersionHelper Class
Modified Calendar style
Modified Clock style
Modified CalendarWithClock Style
Fixed Shake problem of CompareSlider
